sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Action Client
    participant Server as Action Server

    Client->>Server: Send Goal (non-blocking)
    Note over Client: Goal ID returned

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
    Note over Server: Processing Goal...<br/>(may take time)
    Server-->>Client: Feedback #1 (optional)
    Note over Client: Receive Feedback
    Server-->>Client: Feedback #2 (optional)
    Note over Client: Receive Feedback
    end

    Server-->>Client: Result<br/>(Goal completed)
    Note over Client: Handle Result<br/>(success/failure)

    rect rgb(200, 220, 255)
    Note over Client,Server: Key Characteristics:<br/>- Asynchronous/non-blocking<br/>- Goal → Feedback → Result<br/>- Supports long-running tasks<br/>- Real-time feedback during execution
    end
